name: Converse Chuck Taylor All Star Lift Platform Canvas
description: The silhouettes of the Converse Platform high heel shoes that appeared in recent themed collections, are now brought back by Converse in a separate version – the Converse Lift Platform Canvas. If in previous designs, you couldn't help but be moved by the luxurious beauty of this shoe, then in the recent collection, the classic features with the most basic colors will conquer you again. Let's take a look with Drake through the landing of a series of items in the Converse Platform Canvas BST that the basketball house has "loved" selected to send her.
details: Bringing back the high-soled version in a base look, the Converse Lift Platform Canvas is a fluid and harmonious combination of a dense rubber platform and the lightweight, persistent Upper Canvas. With basic colors and hack style that cannot be underestimated, you can confidently wear this item to meet friends in the most beautiful and radiant outfits.

Tổng thể là sự kết hợp của các chi tiết vượt thời gian để trở nên hiện đại nhất. Upper với 50% cotton tái chế và 50% canvas cùng điểm nhấn lượn sóng đầy ấn tượng.
